To bridge the gap between the underlying algorithms and the actual results, here is an in-depth analysis based on the laboratory data [cite: 1].

## 📊 Quantitative Comparison

| Model | Detected Anomalies | Precision | Recall | F1 Score | False Positives (FP) | False Negatives (FN) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Isolation Forest** | 33 | 0.970 | 1.0 | 0.985 | 1 | 0 |
| **Autoencoder + embeddings** | 38 | 0.842 | 1.0 | 0.914 | 6 | 0 |

